1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"周邊都多野玩"},{"pid":"129ea455ee1fcd08cad66cf0bb94e7d6a4e1828d","tid":384023,"uid":73596,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:27:42.000Z","msg":"麗江古城可以靜雞雞唔買飛搏大霧入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b487b46c729ee45a69004ea1f3661e9eb2a83127","tid":384023,"uid":14511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:33:22.000Z","msg":"住束河可能會悶死，太靜<br />\n香格里拉，古城，騎下馬撐下船仔，7日都夠，去埋瀘沽湖揸電單車環湖囉"},{"pid":"1c7e4e5dea0e91602d846d30d957fe13f7a3e313","tid":384023,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:40:24.000Z","msg":"我去過麗江3,4次<br />\n<br />\n結論係，寧願去大理都唔去麗江，寧願去香格里拉都唔去麗江，但麗江夾係中間，有時間都會去一去。"},{"pid":"e1b1723630eeaeb38555ddfae710ae88840afccf","tid":384023,"uid":33174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:44:10.000Z","msg":"幾時啊 留低個tg傾傾"},{"pid":"c272c29e8c6a7835d77d8a0aa5d7d4cd48bdb864","tid":384023,"uid":73596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我去過麗江3,4次<br />\n<br />\n結論係，寧願去大理都唔去麗江，寧願去香格里拉都唔去麗江，但麗江夾係中間，有時間都會去一去。</blockquote><br />\n香格里拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次去，必經之路整到溶溶爛爛，又要勁塞車，上到去真係咩都冇，係咩都冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 浪費咗我兩日時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a14e6d8a92fd98acfc5c25438586179bba76db","tid":384023,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:52:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我去過麗江3,4次<br />\n<br />\n結論係，寧願去大理都唔去麗江，寧願去香格里拉都唔去麗江，但麗江夾係中間，有時間都會去一去。</blockquote><br />\n香格里拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次去，必經之路整到溶溶爛爛，又要勁塞車，上到去真係咩都冇，係咩都冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 浪費咗我兩日時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獨克宗古城雖然之前燒過，但點都寧靜過大理 and麗江古城，睇你想要乜享受<br />\n<br />\n香格里拉有納帕海，有松贊林寺，有普達措國家公園，遠dd可以殺上飛來寺再睇梅里雪山<br />\n<br />\n路爛係睇彩數，你幾時去？我14,15,16年都入過香格里拉，16年甚至係cycling 入去tim,  都唔覺有你d問題<br />\n<br />\n3個地方我都去過唔止一次，麗江古城太多人又太嘈，玉龍雪山真係得啖笑，要排我會咁<br />\n<br />\n香格里拉&gt;大理&gt;麗江"},{"pid":"34d40af810f81f5ff5556e8067465cfd80cf4748","tid":384023,"uid":38662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麗江古城可以靜雞雞唔買飛搏大霧入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成80蚊"},{"pid":"9a11c9376dd056aa072d926644d0b6372b1e3939","tid":384023,"uid":38662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時啊 留低個tg傾傾</blockquote><br />\n下星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6872b2bc4bcd82b1b88ea0aaa3d159c888d741db","tid":384023,"uid":38662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:06:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我去過麗江3,4次<br />\n<br />\n結論係，寧願去大理都唔去麗江，寧願去香格里拉都唔去麗江，但麗江夾係中間，有時間都會去一去。</blockquote><br />\n香格里拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次去，必經之路整到溶溶爛爛，又要勁塞車，上到去真係咩都冇，係咩都冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 浪費咗我兩日時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獨克宗古城雖然之前燒過，但點都寧靜過大理 and麗江古城，睇你想要乜享受<br />\n<br />\n香格里拉有納帕海，有松贊林寺，有普達措國家公園，遠dd可以殺上飛來寺再睇梅里雪山<br />\n<br />\n路爛係睇彩數，你幾時去？我14,15,16年都入過香格里拉，16年甚至係cycling 入去tim,  都唔覺有你d問題<br />\n<br />\n3個地方我都去過唔止一次，麗江古城太多人又太嘈，玉龍雪山真係得啖笑，要排我會咁<br />\n<br />\n香格里拉&gt;大理&gt;麗江</blockquote><br />\n玉龍唔掂？"},{"pid":"914d405c07a502169b58ce34ff7837a243536a4b","tid":384023,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"麗江太商業化"},{"pid":"4d4bf52e92fb176cd31e5edd3b23c16eec9decb1","tid":384023,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>麗江古城可以靜雞雞唔買飛搏大霧入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成80蚊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有好幾個門口，你可以跟大隊入去，有人驗票你就轉另一個門口入，or如果你係住古城入面，可以叫hostel簽張紙比你<br />\n<br />\n我去過幾次都係冇買票"},{"pid":"f38e5a435ed19b80edb97fefc2c50012ade035bc","tid":384023,"uid":142964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:12:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我去過麗江3,4次<br />\n<br />\n結論係，寧願去大理都唔去麗江，寧願去香格里拉都唔去麗江，但麗江夾係中間，有時間都會去一去。</blockquote><br />\n香格里拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次去，必經之路整到溶溶爛爛，又要勁塞車，上到去真係咩都冇，係咩都冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 浪費咗我兩日時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獨克宗古城雖然之前燒過，但點都寧靜過大理 and麗江古城，睇你想要乜享受<br />\n<br />\n香格里拉有納帕海，有松贊林寺，有普達措國家公園，遠dd可以殺上飛來寺再睇梅里雪山<br />\n<br />\n路爛係睇彩數，你幾時去？我14,15,16年都入過香格里拉，16年甚至係cycling 入去tim,  都唔覺有你d問題<br />\n<br />\n3個地方我都去過唔止一次，麗江古城太多人又太嘈，玉龍雪山真係得啖笑，要排我會咁<br />\n<br />\n香格里拉&gt;大理&gt;麗江</blockquote><br />\n玉龍唔掂？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果唔洗錢都可以去下<br />\n要錢？不了。"},{"pid":"258c0db9db79c49c87718be8ea9a320b38925461","tid":384023,"uid":52162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:20:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得如果唔去得長嘅話去麗江會好啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香格里拉喺昆明坐車去有啲遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 麗江係商業化但會多啲嘢睇"},{"pid":"1c0c5bae73c19a57310f66ec52afbf75ab866f79","tid":384023,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:23:07.000Z","msg":"玉龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a3f52ec53d0a876ce454c22420be952e51f080","tid":384023,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"去幾日去來做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1975d7b3490cff45b7d694b4750278f3ef99d069","tid":384023,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去幾日去來做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n麗江唔去幾日唔通留成星期？我諗唔到點解要留咁耐.....冇乜太多野睇and玩，你話日日入古城酒吧街yo女交配就另計啦。"},{"pid":"93872cbdfdddddb88c57d7333f3bb1582182f880","tid":384023,"uid":137282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:29:52.000Z","msg":"其實可以去虎跳峽過一晚<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/03/012808_f51b4283fcded53a4f99c56c999422c5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F03%2F012808_f51b4283fcded53a4f99c56c999422c5.JPG&h=0ba0c637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/03/012922_3d67b989f9d17bba0ae223d88134e59f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F03%2F012922_3d67b989f9d17bba0ae223d88134e59f.JPG&h=cb515849&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c77ab4a06914fdc1b0dfde17719a5f061aa5fa8","tid":384023,"uid":52418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:43:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf4d26f355e8b7cd45eff44b7ef9b22ab38e70eb","tid":384023,"uid":52418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:45:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fef2b5e6511b2cf9f78bfb792a555afa866e9e92","tid":384023,"uid":139322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>麗江古城可以靜雞雞唔買飛搏大霧入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成80蚊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有好幾個門口，你可以跟大隊入去，有人驗票你就轉另一個門口入，or如果你係住古城入面，可以叫hostel簽張紙比你<br />\n<br />\n我去過幾次都係冇買票</blockquote><br />\n有個無人看守既入口好似近街市果面...<br />\n試過果到入幾次...但好易行錯<br />\n同埋班友見你樣唔似大陸人就會問你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前去....好多大陸樣既人直行直過,我諗住博大霧,一行過去就問我有無買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74657de62f5bb5c0ec2fc3d2106e3597c661bf8","tid":384023,"uid":83920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:09:54.000Z","msg":"一定 去埋大理 👍"},{"pid":"c5112ba89c487254062ca8d294db28e1b86ece21","tid":384023,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:47:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去幾日去來做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n麗江唔去幾日唔通留成星期？我諗唔到點解要留咁耐.....冇乜太多野睇and玩，你話日日入古城酒吧街yo女交配就另計啦。</blockquote><br />\n意思咪係去得幾日,特登去麗江,去來做乜9,周街都係呢D酒吧商業街啦......廣州就有,駛乜特登去麗江<br />\n要去就至少都十日啦,瀘沽湖 中虎跳, 香格里拉 大理, 呢D大路行程<br />\n<br />\n去我幾日剩去麗江=on9行為"},{"pid":"e7b0649543e24322fea8de8546794e02c79e3ab8","tid":384023,"uid":142325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T21:36:10.000Z","msg":"聽個北京妹講失戀既人會去麗江，有機會有艷遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf6a96322f77f10486bc1a7f7c4d617fe79425d","tid":384023,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T03:16:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>麗江古城可以靜雞雞唔買飛搏大霧入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成80蚊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有好幾個門口，你可以跟大隊入去，有人驗票你就轉另一個門口入，or如果你係住古城入面，可以叫hostel簽張紙比你<br />\n<br />\n我去過幾次都係冇買票</blockquote><br />\n係我真心定點<br />\n麗江唔洗買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d28c89817e205e5ce6850216f9abc2dce3e35e","tid":384023,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T03:17:38.000Z","msg":"淨係去麗江古城一定好撚悶,極之商業化<br />\n隔離束河古鎮仲有特色<br />\n不過兩個加埋頂盡兩日<br />\nbtw 麗江依家已經取消左唔洗買飛"},{"pid":"e7f350ff97e86d5559e9787d0c65a83df34c9b41","tid":384023,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T03:29:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係去麗江古城一定好撚悶,極之商業化<br />\n隔離束河古鎮仲有特色<br />\n不過兩個加埋頂盡兩日<br />\nbtw 麗江依家已經取消左唔洗買飛</blockquote><br />\n比人屌得太多，好似鳳凰古城咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e091a1d5746c98820be3ad7ea084a8d880554ac","tid":384023,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>麗江古城可以靜雞雞唔買飛搏大霧入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成80蚊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有好幾個門口，你可以跟大隊入去，有人驗票你就轉另一個門口入，or如果你係住古城入面，可以叫hostel簽張紙比你<br />\n<br />\n我去過幾次都係冇買票</blockquote><br />\n係我真心定點<br />\n麗江唔洗買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要買票入古城，你冇買係因為你逃票咁解<br />\n<br />\n等於你搭地鐵都可以唔買飛tim,  但佢本身有規定要買飛先入"},{"pid":"589fe7abaa9207d036f616b7395056a053f66540","tid":384023,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:08:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係去麗江古城一定好撚悶,極之商業化<br />\n隔離束河古鎮仲有特色<br />\n不過兩個加埋頂盡兩日<br />\nbtw 麗江依家已經取消左唔洗買飛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n16年仲要，17年洗唔洗唔清楚lu"},{"pid":"1ebf213f4d04303432a393daebae0281e43eec29","tid":384023,"uid":9741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:12:15.000Z","msg":"前2日先係麗江返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4fa0fd66e38c37440372934a9b84a295e8c414","tid":384023,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:26:55.000Z","msg":"中學果陣跟學校去過<br />\n由昆明一路上到香格里拉<br />\n麗江, 大理, 普洱果 d 都有去"},{"pid":"66768f878116a20e629ca2e9fde3cf3952e72e01","tid":384023,"uid":38662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:58:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淨係麗江會唔會悶<br />\n拎唔到好多日假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨麗係會. <br />\n去週邊就唔會.<br />\n<br />\n除非你係仔,日日食雞.<br />\n聽講麗江好多艷遇.</blockquote><br />\n不了食雞<br />\n冇咁多日假去咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef47d0d01abccb078073bd00176bd5fcd5003c45","tid":384023,"uid":38662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:59:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前2日先係麗江返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗唔洗飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1419d666e48280a94fc2145de64a73be64f86aed","tid":384023,"uid"