"pid":"7c68aaea07adf7bf78f4365a79b5f42ab1a812ec","tid":384023,"uid":52418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c12b37c38234c1ffcfff3e60edff65ed565200c","tid":384023,"uid":21557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T00:01:41.000Z","msg":"9號飛昆明 咩都未plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e88af283006537ceaeb99fad0e990d323b5abc","tid":384023,"uid":104081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b805120bbd0f96469b7e7914e5a6fd9526f586a","tid":384023,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過兩次麗江, 唔會去第三次<br />\n第二次去商業化到爆<br />\n成條街係度播一瞬間同一窩蜂賣果隻鼓<br />\n香格里拉正好多</blockquote><br />\nSICK 野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊去多次香格里拉入雨崩"},{"pid":"9c0a4d5a2a6a8f9c1fab7171e99b5c031dfa9156","tid":384023,"uid":104081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T16:08:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4eb339adce292b601e0e64ae584b60f26a67f5f","tid":384023,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去過兩次麗江, 唔會去第三次<br />\n第二次去商業化到爆<br />\n成條街係度播一瞬間同一窩蜂賣果隻鼓<br />\n香格里拉正好多</blockquote><br />\nSICK 野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊去多次香格里拉入雨崩</blockquote><br />\n正呀，我上次入雨崩果時，係飛來寺睇唔到日照金頂，有啲可惜。但入到雨崩村好靚，世外桃源咁，第二日上冰湖仲見到對面山雪崩好震撼，第三日上神瀑又係好靚。原本走果時想係尼農走，但當地人話前一日山泥傾瀉好危險，睇相尼農果度，另一邊就係懸崖，不得了</blockquote><br />\n姐係巴打最後原路出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日照金山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b006cdb8f5c993e4708bef132019c5b82b1c4d","tid":384023,"uid":38662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:18:22.000Z","msg":"聽朝早機去麗江<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb54cdf956f90c5d000bf099431b215704ed7614","tid":384023,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:20:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去過兩次麗江, 唔會去第三次<br />\n第二次去商業化到爆<br />\n成條街係度播一瞬間同一窩蜂賣果隻鼓<br />\n香格里拉正好多</blockquote><br />\nSICK 野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊去多次香格里拉入雨崩</blockquote><br />\n正呀，我上次入雨崩果時，係飛來寺睇唔到日照金頂，有啲可惜。但入到雨崩村好靚，世外桃源咁，第二日上冰湖仲見到對面山雪崩好震撼，第三日上神瀑又係好靚。原本走果時想係尼農走，但當地人話前一日山泥傾瀉好危險，睇相尼農果度，另一邊就係懸崖，不得了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尼農而家條路都幾闊，唔係落雨天既話都幾安全。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/05/092039_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F05%2F092039_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=571a1342&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e79a13cc52e887944323f94fb496b29bdf07168","tid":384023,"uid":104081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:58:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"478cd22ac664f7810ff5c1d85ea4722e6c9048e9","tid":384023,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:20:35.000Z","msg":"古城d bar 既酒應該係溝晒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2b09fbe3218f87324ce28225938d9f5dc4d24f","tid":384023,"uid":38662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古城d bar 既酒應該係溝晒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc348196794af17491391e5c3081da3bb4342ffe","tid":384023,"uid":38662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:54:09.000Z","msg":"準備去到就報團<br />\n淨係報一個既話<br />\n玉龍/拉市/虎跳 邊個好"},{"pid":"7a9f00f0cfe85268e141fe8427dbc